WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.070 --> 00:00:03.493
<v ->Dr. Robert Scaer knows trauma.</v>

2
00:00:03.493 --> 00:00:06.433
As a child he experienced many life-altering events,

3
00:00:06.433 --> 00:00:08.933
not the least of which was losing his left eye

4
00:00:08.933 --> 00:00:11.353
after it was pierced with a coat hanger.

5
00:00:11.353 --> 00:00:13.133
He ultimately became a neurologist,

6
00:00:13.133 --> 00:00:14.553
dedicating his life to the alleviation

7
00:00:14.553 --> 00:00:16.903
of pain and suffering.

8
00:00:16.903 --> 00:00:20.203
Dr. Scaer's new book," The Trauma Spectrum:

9
00:00:20.203 --> 00:00:22.343
"Hidden Wounds and Human Resiliency",

10
00:00:22.343 --> 00:00:24.923
