11
00:00:24.923 --> 00:00:26.883
that shape our life experience,

12
00:00:26.883 --> 00:00:29.863
rather, little everyday traumas that impact

13
00:00:29.863 --> 00:00:33.043
all facets of our daily lives and inner experience.

14
00:00:33.043 --> 00:00:35.603
