19
00:00:51.143 --> 00:00:54.003
traumatized to one degree or another?

20
00:00:54.003 --> 00:00:55.503
<v ->100%.</v>

21
00:00:55.503 --> 00:00:56.883
<v Voiceover>100%.</v>
<v ->Yes.</v>

22
00:00:56.883 --> 00:00:58.443
